title: Foreign Minister holds a phone call with the Vice-President of the Libyan Presidential Council
text: Minister of Foreign Affairs, Mr Sabri Boukadoum, today, had a telephone conversation with the Vice-President of the Libyan Presidential Council, Mr Moussa al-Kouni.

The two officials discussed ways and means of strengthening economic relations between the two countries and smoothing out the difficulties facing businessmen on both sides, as well as the prospects for relaunching the political process for the settlement of the crisis in this brother country.
